在改良式當事人進行主義下，逐漸重視法庭活動之活絡，而彈劾證據之運用即在此展現。作為認定實體犯罪事實之證據，有嚴格證明法則作為規範；那麼，作為減損或是回復證人可信度之彈劾證據，是否有相關規範，即是本文討論重點。其中，又以「彈劾證據之適用範圍」為核心問題。對於彈劾證據之規範，係以美國聯邦證據法、習慣法以及日本法作為參考對象，進而斟酌我國實務情況，對規範方式提出自己見解。對於爭議問題，係以建立實質公平法院為核心價值，採取衡平觀點。

This study aims to investigating credibility of witnesses’ attack and rehabilitation. Moreover, the author intends to discover the scope of application for impeachment evidence. Finally, judgments were examined in the study to offer an appropriate solution. Based on the U.S. Federal Rule of Evidence, common law, and Japanese law, this study is to explicate the issues of impeachment evidence. The results of this study were that the scope of impeachment evidence must take judicial practice into consideration to reach the goal of equal justice.

